    "description": "TOSNET Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, provides security services in Japan. The company offers static guard services for office buildings, stores, parking lots, banks, warehouses, residences, etc.; crowd control services for festivals, concerts, sporting games, conventions, seminars, parades, expos, shop's openings, etc.; traffic control services for parking lots, construction sites, warehouses, etc.; and retail security services for grocery stores, jewelry shops, department stores, appliance stores, etc. It also provides power supply car services for events, concerts, sporting games, blackouts, data centers, and business continuity plans; mailing services; and building management, equipment maintenance, and cleaning services. In addition, the company offers automated external defibrillators under ZOLLR AED PlusR brand. The company also involved in power supply business. It serves customers through its network of branch offices. TOSNET Corporation was incorporated in 1977 and is headquartered in Sendai, Japan."
